ury.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 25. Nov 2020) 0aCollective memoryzChinaxHistory. 4aChina. 4aHistory. 4aTaiping Rebellion (1850-1864). 4acommemoration. 4adestruction. 4apost-war reconstruction. 4awartime suffering. 7aHISTORY / Asia / China.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUP Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311070420440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780804785594zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804785594423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780804785594.jpg  a978-3-11-070420-4  SUP Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles